headline: PayPal Could Still Be 20% Too Cheap - Use Options to Play PYPL
summary: PayPal stock could be 20% too cheap, based on management's free cash flow guidance and an average FCF yield metric. Investors can short out-of-the-money puts and calls, as well as buy long-dated in-the-money calls to play PYPL.
